Love love LOVE Evo lounge. Went on two Thursdays during Happy Hour around like 4-5pm. Its usually slow in the lounge around this time so if you're looking for a space for you and/or friend(s) to have drinks and apps without a huge crowd of people this is the perfect time and place for you.  The apps and regular drinks (like Martinis, Margaritas etc) are only $5 dollars and I'm in LOVE. Our bartender last week Thursday (4/4) named Corey made this tasty strawberry-mango margarita for me and this Black Label whiskey sour for my fiance and it was everything! He was very attentive and always checked on us to make sure we were alright despite the fact that they had other responsibilities to take care of. My favorite happy hour apps are the chicken nachos and the sweet chili wings.  There are two bartenders that will (more than likely) be there during this time; Corey and Delissa! Shes so sweet, efficient, her makeup is always on point (lol), she smiles alot and always makes sure we're taken care of. Both of these two has made my experience at Evo exceptional.  Love the decor and spacious bar and dining area.  Would 10/10 reccomend this place.
